subject: Dear Sir,
body:
Dear Sir,
Good day, can you please get back to me because i have important issues to discuss with you.
Regards
Phillip

subject: Re: Dear Sir,
body:
Dear Phillip,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I'm always open to discussing important matters. Could you please provide me with more details about the issues you would like to discuss? I want to make sure I can assist you in the best possible way.

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Eddy
